<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>자포스 on OpenMicroLab</title><link>https://openmicrolab.com/tags/%EC%9E%90%ED%8F%AC%EC%8A%A4/</link><description>Recent content in 자포스 on OpenMicroLab</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>ko</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Sep 2010 02:36:44 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://openmicrolab.com/tags/%EC%9E%90%ED%8F%AC%EC%8A%A4/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>행복을 파는 회사 자포스 (Zappos)의 핵심가치</title><link>https://openmicrolab.com/%ED%96%89%EB%B3%B5%EC%9D%84-%ED%8C%8C%EB%8A%94-%ED%9A%8C%EC%82%AC-%EC%9E%90%ED%8F%AC%EC%8A%A4-zappos%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC%EA%B0%80%EC%B9%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Sep 2010 02:36:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://openmicrolab.com/%ED%96%89%EB%B3%B5%EC%9D%84-%ED%8C%8C%EB%8A%94-%ED%9A%8C%EC%82%AC-%EC%9E%90%ED%8F%AC%EC%8A%A4-zappos%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC%EA%B0%80%EC%B9%98/</guid><description>
&lt;p>&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; ">&lt;/p>&lt;/p>
&lt;div>
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; ">&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">대부분의 회사의 존재 이유는 이유추구입니다.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Gulim; font-size: 15px; ">하지만 회사내 모든 가치판단의 기준이 이윤이 되버리면 직원들은 힘들어하고 스트레스를 받지 않을 수 없습니다.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Gulim; font-size: 15px; ">즉 마케팅이나 영업은 매월 매출 실적에 따라 안절 부절하고, R&amp;D는 정해진 기한에 제품을 만들기 위해 진정으로 고객이 원하는 것이 무엇인지를 간과하기도 합니다.&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; ">&lt;br /> &lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; ">&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">회사가 커짐에 따라 회사의 핵심가치를 정의하는 것은 중요한데,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; ">&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">아마존에 합병된 자포스(Zappos)의 홈페이지에는 이 회사의 핵심가치를 10가지로 정의하고 각 항목마다 자세한 설명 페이지가 있습니다.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; ">&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">&lt;br /> &lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 굴림; line-height: 18px; font-size: 12px; ">&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://openmicrolab.com/images/1/cfile4.uf.135F21264C88439A6B2CDA.jpg" class="aligncenter" width="640" height="659" alt="" filename="cfile4.uf.135F21264C88439A6B2CDA.jpg" filemime="" />&lt;br /> &lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div style="text-align: center;">
&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 굴림; line-height: 18px; font-size: 12px; ">&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">&lt;a href="http://about.zappos.com/our-unique-culture/zappos-core-values">http://about.zappos.com/our-unique-culture/zappos-core-values&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;font class="Apple-style-span" face="Gulim" size="4">&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px;">이 회사의&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/font>&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">&lt;a href="http://blogs.zappos.com/" target="_blank" title="[http://blogs.zappos.com/]로 이동합니다.">블로그&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">를 보면 자포스와&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Gulim; font-size: 15px; ">CEO인 토니의 생각을 알 수 있습니다.&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;font class="Apple-style-span" face="Gulim" size="4">&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px;">&lt;br /> &lt;/span>&lt;/font>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div>
&lt;span style="font-size: 11pt; ">&lt;span style="font-family: Gulim; ">&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://openmicrolab.com/images/1/cfile30.uf.147104274C8843CE53A040.jpg" class="aligncenter" width="680" height="158" alt="" filename="Zappos2.jpg" filemime="image/jpeg" />블로그 위의 이미지에 있는 트위터 글도 명언이네요&amp;#8230;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/div>
